    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sr-Rainbow Trout Oligopeptide-1 sh-Polypeptide-11 is a single chain fusion peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from sr-Rainbow Trout Oligopeptide-1 and sh-Polypeptide-11. The fusion peptide contains 154 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acid."
